  "texts": [
    "An LLM can even be used to produce summaries of internal documents, for example meeting minutes, if meeting participants give their consent and no confidential information was shared (Rule 4).",
    "To facilitate this process, speech-to-text transcription software can first be used to produce a full written record of a meeting.",
    "Then, this transcribed meeting can be shared with the LLM, which can be tasked with producing a summary.",
    "For this use, the adequacy of the summary should of course be verified by the meeting participants to ensure that important points have not been left out nor misrepresented.",
    "Use an LLM to refine written English in formal and informal communication."
  ],
